    <item>
      <title>Nexus: Multi-Agent RAG Intelligence</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/mypage/nexus/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/mypage/nexus/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://project-nexus.duckdns.org/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;🚀 Launch Live Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;   |   &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/bellerophon95/nexus&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;📁 View Source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;143 commits. 8 active days. Zero to production on AWS.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Solo-built from a blank repository to a deployed, multi-agent AI platform — including three hosting pivots in 48 hours.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-problem&#34;&gt;&#xA;  The Problem&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#the-problem&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Traditional RAG systems are often &amp;ldquo;black boxes&amp;rdquo; — they retrieve documents and generate answers with no transparency into &lt;em&gt;why&lt;/em&gt; a specific piece of context was chosen or whether the final answer is actually grounded in truth. This lack of observability makes them unsuitable for high-stakes research or decision support.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
